The paper discusses large-scale distributed cooperative systems, which suggests a focus on distributed computing (cs.DC). The use of optimistic replication and the design of a commitment protocol suggest a focus on databases (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The mention of semantic constraints and the representation of the system as a graph suggest a focus on software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY).
